:0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"你叫班舊制去做算啦<br />\n新制得個十幾日假賺得個兩千幾雞碎咁多又要請多日假<br />\n班大粒野可以去到兩皮幾野又大把假請<br />\n你自己做飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69c95db0b8ab27f2c4df99fed923ce27711a5c7","tid":1685474,"uid":5502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec10a3f913a7298839943519d3ba1023592fff61","tid":1685474,"uid":179718,"like":194,"dislike":3,"score":191,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"又吹水<br />\n招聘係 4 月嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜事都未發生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"之前立會搞到勁夜，已經有班老野怕左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家D人係出左offer之後話唔做"},{"pid":"38e85ad46ad45eaa02b559afc475abd95e0e83c1","tid":1685474,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80ffdfbcc75f1b597e3310ac2b754b53f5d018d1","tid":1685474,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c0f259f95e0ef88da9f56694985e018fd19e157","tid":1685474,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:20:51.000Z","msg":"2016做左超級區議會，<br />\n晚上9點入去， 第二日晚上7點先出返黎，<br />\n唔好再預我。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f57867c919216f740b220cb30bc18871913a31","tid":1685474,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"假新聞<br />\n一早就開始請人<br />\n驚乜衝擊票站"},{"pid":"143fbde487957608530d367040021a06ac0d7773","tid":1685474,"uid":49359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8bdabd1bc13b4d673197c0c7cd694